    <briefdescription>
<para>ADC hardware abstraction public API. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This driver provides an interface for reading analog values from the ADC peripherals. It returns raw conversion values, typically 10–12 bits depending on the hardware. </para>
